We’ve never known before—

00:56:18.870 --> 00:56:24.876 line:90% position:50% align:center
A world ruled
by justice and love.

00:56:24.876 --> 00:56:31.633 line:90% position:50% align:center
To the ends of the earth,
There’ll be peace at last

00:56:31.633 --> 00:56:37.514 line:90% position:50% align:center
For all eternity.

00:56:37.514 --> 00:56:44.980 line:90% position:50% align:center
From the valleys below
