00:58:06.438 --> 00:58:14.446 line:90% position:50% align:center
Peace at last!

00:58:20.953 --> 00:58:23.080 line:90% position:50% align:center
What a beautiful song!

00:58:23.080 --> 00:58:26.667 line:90% position:50% align:center
And what beautiful images to encourage us!

00:58:26.667 --> 00:58:31.547 line:90% position:50% align:center
So brothers and sisters, we’ve enjoyed
our convention program, haven’t we?

00:58:31.547 --> 00:58:35.384 line:90% position:50% align:center
Let us be determined to keep pursuing peace,

00:58:35.384 --> 00:58:39.263 line:90% position:50% align:center
not an imitation peace, but the real peace.

00:58:39.263 --> 00:58:41.807 line:90% position:50% align:center
We can enjoy rich blessings now

00:58:41.807 --> 00:58:45.353 line:90% position:50% align:center
by having a peaceful relationship
with Jehovah God,

00:58:45.353 --> 00:58:49.482 line:90% position:50% align:center
yes, trying to continue
to maintain peace with one another

00:58:49.482 --> 00:58:54.320 line:90% position:50% align:center
and also attaining to this inner peace
—calmness and tranquility—

00:58:54.320 --> 00:58:58.950 line:90% position:50% align:center
because we have friendship
with the God who gives us hope.

00:58:58.950 --> 00:59:02.078 line:90% position:50% align:center
And that hope helps us to look to the future,

00:59:02.078 --> 00:59:04.372 line:90% position:50% align:center
even though we have difficulties now,

00:59:04.372 --> 00:59:06.541 line:90% position:50% align:center
and we look forward to the time

00:59:06.541 --> 00:59:10.670 line:90% position:50% align:center
when universal peace is finally restored.

00:59:10.670 --> 00:59:14.173 line:90% position:50% align:center
But in the meantime, may the God of peace

00:59:14.173 --> 00:59:18.469 line:90% position:50% align:center
be with each one of you now and forever!

